# Diagram Index

This directory contains visual diagrams used throughout the BRM and Stable Thinking Stack documentation.

The diagrams illustrate structural concepts such as:

- AI collaboration failures
- prompt dissolution
- structural reasoning anchors
- Branching Reference Model behavior
- long-term conversation stability

These figures are referenced across the documentation to explain how AI collaboration evolves during extended interaction.

---

